val distribution business and the owner of a major competing newspaper title.{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s19\cf0\sl240\slmult1\qj\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\cf3  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs20\lang7177\i0\b0\ltrch\hich\f4\fs20\loch\f4\fs20 See arbitration transcript at pp 281-7 of the record of these proceedings.  King\'92s insistence that his group had over the very many years of its existence built up a distribution system, in which information was a critical competitive asset, one that to s
