tors cannot reasonably provide goods or services to their customers.\'92}{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s19\cf0\sl240\slmult1\qj\rtlch\af3\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af3\langfe255\hich\f4\fs20\lang7177\loch\f4\fs20\lang7177 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs20\lang7177\i0\b0 Competition Act Section 1(1)(viii)}}}
